description: Cut from the rump, this steak has a strong, meaty flavour and a firm bite.Cooking hint & tips:PREP: Remove steak from fridge and rest it to room temperature before cooking.SEASON & SEAR: Lightly oil and season well with salt & pepper. Sear in a hot pan to seal in the juices. Tip: If cooking over a BBQ grill, do not oil your steak to avoid burning.REST: Rest before serving for a more tender and juicy experience.Level of Doneness:Pan Fry/BBQ:Rare - 2.5 min on each side and rest for 2 minutesMedium - 3.5 min each side and rest for 4 minutes (recommended)Well done- 5.5 minutes on each side, rest for 5 minutes
name: Woolworths Beef Rump Steak Medium 270G  750G
